^xE05030 ^7Hey all!^7 ^x70FF70Ronarray^7 here and this is ^x70FF70^7my ^x70FF70^xD02090^x7070FF^7^xB97123STEP BY STEP^7 ^xE05030Bleed Lacerate Gladiator^xFFFF77 League Starter Build^7 ^7Guide! If you like the guide please make sure to Like the video as well - subscribe to the ^xE05030YouTube channel^7 for more content too! If you have questions or want to discuss anything build related - feel free to hit me on Twitch or discord, I will be glad to help.
^x70FF70 Discord^7 https://discord.gg/xDQVEQahMT
^x70FF70Twitch^7 https://www.twitch.tv/ronarray
^x70FF70YouTube^7 https://www.youtube.com/@ronarray
|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| ^xE05030 ^x70FF70 Tips ^7|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|^7^7
^x70FF701.^7^xE05030 ^7^xAF6025^7While leveling prioritize weapons with higher DPS, mostly axes at all times.^7 It is ^xE05030important^7 so try to change weapons often.
^x70FF702.^7^7 Make sure to always have a^xE05030 Life leech^7 / ^x3F6DB3Mana Leech^7 either from Tree or Gloves or Belt. Especially after Act 5 - Look into mana issues Timestamp in the video for help. ^7^7 ^x70FF703.^7 ^x8888FF^7^xE05030Vulnerability ^7is the main curse and great DPS boost - use it on all single targets that can survive a few seconds. ^7We are keeping it self cast but Reckoning Option could be possible later.
^x70FF704.^7 ^x7070FF^7If you have mana issues especially early on dont fortget to use^x7070FF Clarity^7, dont level it further than a level that wil lfix your issues. ^x70FF70 5.^7 Flasks in the setup are not too optimized and just my basic choice that I have used while leveling and progressing through atlas. Feel free to change them but Keep at least Basalt.
^x70FF706.^7 Everything else you can find in the video - please check TIMESTAMPS that I have created for easier navigation.
^x70FF707.^7 If you still have questions - hit me on twitch, link is up there. ^x70FF70^7 |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|^7^7 ^x70FF70Thank you for checking the build out!^x70FF70 ^7^x70FF70Wish you a great league start^7^7!^7 ^x70FF70Please like the video and subscribe to the channel if you enjoyed it.^7 |-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------| ^x70FF70
